---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
const title = 'Speech to Text';
---

<DocsLayout title={title}>
<h1>Speech to Text</h1>
<p>Transcribe audio files using <code>POST /v1/stt</code> with multipart form data.</p>
<pre><code>{`curl -X POST http://localhost:18645/v1/stt \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $API_KEY" \
  -F "file=@recording.mp3" \
  -F "language=en" \
  -F "diarize=true"`}</code></pre>
<table>
<tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr>
<tr><td>file</td><td>file</td><td>Audio file to transcribe (multipart upload)</td></tr>
<tr><td>language</td><td>string</td><td>Language code (e.g. en, ko, ja)</td></tr>
<tr><td>diarize</td><td>boolean</td><td>Enable speaker diarization</td></tr>
</table>
</DocsLayout>
